<HEADLINE>
FT  16 FEB 94 / UK Company News: Kwik-Fit expands with tyre fitting buy
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
Kwik-Fit has acquired a 70 per cent interest in Town &amp; Country Tyre
Services, the UK's largest mobile car tyre fitting company.
Town &amp; Country operates a fleet of 27 vehicles in and around London, which
Kwik-Fit intends to expand to 150 vehicles.
Kwik-Fit has also completed the sale and leaseback of 20 centres to
Dukeminster, a property investor, on 30-year leases with rents of Pounds 1m
a year. Consideration was Pounds 10.3m cash.
</TEXT>
