GDP per worker                         +23           +6.5
Total employment manufacturing          +3           -4.5
Employment                              +5          -18
Real wages                             +16           +9
Consumer prices                        +13          +30.5
Investment                             +11.5         -7.5
Personal consumption                   +16           +3.5
 -----------------------------------------------------------------------
